ous attempts to go beyond the standard quantum theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 1999 16:19:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 1999 10:29:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-26"}
